data.text:
There are several hundreds of car brands, from immensely popular makes to small and defunct ones. Even those who work in the automotive industry do not know each and every brand, to say nothing of their history, specialization, and model range.

This page provides an alphabetically sorted list of car brands from all corners of the world. The list includes not only most popular and familiar makes, but also lesser known ones. If you look through the page, you will surely find a lot of names you have never heard about. For the most known automakers, there is not only the name of the brand, but also the logo.
